                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8184" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1270</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1571 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">校门到舱门——桂林机场一站式直达服务流程优化之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">School Gate to Cabin Gate: The Road to Optimizing the One Stop Direct Service Flow at Guilin Airport</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙瑜，邓榕榕，党园</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湘潭大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西机场管理集团桂林两江国际机场有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务流程优化；协同优化；服务蓝图</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Service Flow Optimization; Collaborative Optimization; Service Blueprint</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“十四五”规划提出以提升便利度和改善服务体验为导向，推动服务业向高品质和多样化升级。民航业作为服务业的重要产业之一，如何提升服务品质、促进服务高质量发展成为民航业发展的重要问题之一。为落实民航局提出的“真情服务”理念，2017年，航服公司以公路运输服务的延伸为契机，以桂林高校师生出行需求为基础，推出“校门到舱门”服务。至今，该服务流程优化至师生旅客出行全过程（预约、值机、安检）。本案例旨在以服务流程优化的角度，剖析“校门到舱门”服务“从0到1”和“从1到N”的全过程。本案例希望学员通过深入了解企业服务流程优化的关键因素、实现步骤和优化工具，从而评价服务流程优化的效果，并对服务业思考如何持续优化服务流程具有借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The &quot;14th Five-Year Plan&quot; proposes to enhance convenience and improve service experiences, promoting the high-quality and diversified development of the service industry. As the important sectors within the service industry, the civil aviation industry faces the crucial task of improving service quality and facilitating high-quality service development. In order to implement the concept of &quot;sincere service&quot; advocated by the CAA, in 2017, the Company took the opportunity of extending its services to include ground transportation and launched the &quot;From Campus to Cabin&quot; service, based on the travel needs of students and faculties from universities in Guilin. This service has been continuously optimized to cover every step of the passenger journey, including reservation, check-in, and security screening. This case study aims to analyze the entire process of developing the &quot;From Campus to Cabin&quot; service, from its inception (&quot;from 0 to 1&quot;) to its expansion (&quot;from 1 to N&quot;), focusing on service process optimization. It encourages students to evaluate the effectiveness of service process optimization by gaining a deeper understanding of key factors, implementation steps, and optimization tools. Furthermore, it provokes thoughts on how to continuously improve service processes in the service industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《流程管理》、《服务营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务流程；服务流程优化；协同优化；服务蓝图</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-03</td>
                            </tr>
